items.title: How to use present tenses - 6 Minute Grammar
The secret of giraffes' long legs. Learn: spindly, hindrance, evolutionary, modestly proportioned
Ivory protest. Learn: ornaments, confiscated, illegal, slaughtered, crushed
Monuments in Nepal reopen. Learn: devastation, heritage, precarious, cash-strapped, kick-start
Oil painting copy shop. Learn: masterpieces, mass-produced, replicas, revenue, original
